  <steps>
    <step num="0">In a food processor, combine the avocado, lime juice, garlic, salt, and water. Pulse until smooth, then transfer to a large mason jar. </step>
    <step num="1">Add the bell pepper, corn, cherry tomatoes, quinoa, black beans, and spinach and screw on the lid. </step>
    <step num="2">Store in the refrigerator until ready to eat, up to 5 days. </step>
    <step num="3">Give the mason jar a good shake to mix and use a fork or spoon to stir as needed. </step>
    <step num="4">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
